%e A324038 The successors of T(1,1) = 5 == 5 (mod 6) are (2*5 - 1)/3 = 3 and 4*5 + 1 = 21. The successor of T(2, 1) = 3 == 3 (mod 6) is 4*3 + 1 = 13. The successors of T(3, 1) = 13 == 1 (mod 6) are (4*13 - 1)/3 = 17 and 4*13 + 1 = 53.
